race.description: Half Yours Melbourne Cup Winner F&M Handicap
race.comment: OUT OF SQUARE (1) resumes off a sharp jumpout success and is a proven fresh performer with a strong record at this distance. Gets weight relief under the 3kg claimer and looks to have a class edge. IN LOVE (4) showed plenty of grit when leading pillar-to-post at Balaklava and has been kept up to the mark with a jumpout win since. In light at the weights with the claimer sticking, he'll give backers another bold sight. MISS KERMIE (3) has trialled stylishly in readiness. Suspect she can run a big race fresh. MAJESTICITY (5) hasn't broken through this campaign but has been around the mark and carries a fitness edge. KINETIC JEWEL (2) was too bad to be true fresh and has since been back to the trials. Capable of sharp improvement and shouldn't be underestimated.
